rnance\", \"from\": 4921, \"to\": 4936}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Boxing at the Paris Games is being run by officials appointed by the IOC, which said it is using rule books based on the version that applied at the 2016 Rio de Janeiro Olympics.\", \"from\": 4940, \"to\": 5118, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5009, \"end\": 5012, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.207643248843933e-33, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 4950, \"to\": 4965}, {\"ngram\": \"officials\", \"from\": 4982, \"to\": 4991}, {\"ngram\": \"rule books\", \"from\": 5037, \"to\": 5047}, {\"ngram\": \"the version\", \"from\": 5057, \"to\": 5068}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2016 Rio de Janeiro Olympics\", \"from\": 5085, \"to\": 5117}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 2025 Sky UK\", \"from\": 5120, \"to\": 5133, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5127, \"end\": 5133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sky UK\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00a9\", \"from\": 5120, \"to\": 5121}]}]}"